name: Super Cartoon Run 3D:2019
description:
It is a new version of a game.
"SUPER CARTOON RUN 3D:2019",
We are providing different characters to run on snow environment. Collect coins and for every 18*2 count, multiple coins will be added, so you can use these coins to buy new characters. We've power ups in the game. If you touch the obstacles, the game will be end..!
"ENJOY THE GAME"
